  "The boxplots look similar because both classes have roughly the same range of test score values": "",
  "Class B scored higher overall, which is the only relevant comparison that can be made from boxplots": "",
  "Class A is better because it has no outliers, making its score distribution more desirable and reliable": "",
  "A complete comparison addresses center (medians), spread (IQRs), and unusual features (outliers) for both groups.": "",
